<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gossip-vi">gossip <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡɒsɪp/    美 /'ɡɑːsɪp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>散布流言：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can't stand here gossiping all day.
我不能整天站在这儿闲聊。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She's been <strong>gossiping about</strong> you.
她一直在说你的闲话。</p></div></div>